== Emirates or United Arab Emirates Country ==

Emirates is a country established by joining of seven states located in south of Persian Gulf. Althogh these seven states are united, each state has its own government and some local laws and rules.
The ruler of each state is called Sheikh.

[http://www.emirates.com Emirates] or [http://www.emirates.com Emirates Airline] is also name for one of the official airline of the country.

